OL,3,CMother's fight to reopen the case of
OL,4,Cher son's death
OL,6,FSpeaking to S4C's current affairs
OL,7,Fprogramme , his mother, Melanie
OL,8,FTookey, said: "We are completely
OL,9,Fdisappointed, it's a terrible feeling.
OL,10,FWe are not convinced that the
OL,11,Finvestigation should be over."
OL,13,FNorth Wales Police have provided
OL,14,FMelanie with an explanation for what
OL,15,Fthey believe had happened to Josh, but
OL,16,Fshe says that it does not give her a
OL,17,Fclear picture of what exactly happened
OL,18,Fto her son.
