OL,3,CMother's fight to reopen the case of
OL,4,Cher son's death
OL,6,FThe details of the police's
OL,7,Finvestigation cannot be revealed as
OL,8,Fthis could impact any potential legal
OL,9,Fproceedings in the future. But Melanie
OL,10,Ffeels that their explanation still
OL,11,Fleft her with unanswered questions.
OL,13,F"Are they challenging the people they
OL,14,Farrested enough? Did they do full
OL,15,Fforensic checks on all the cars? Did
OL,16,Fthey do a drug test in addition to a
OL,17,Fbreathalyser?" She said.
