OL,3,CMother's fight to reopen the case of
OL,4,Cher son's death
OL,6,FFollowing the decision by North Wales
OL,7,FPolice to close the case, Melanie was
OL,8,Finformed that she had three months to
OL,9,Fsubmit an application to request a
OL,10,Freview of the case.
OL,12,F"Josh is not here to stand up for
OL,13,Fhimself, and we are not going to let
OL,14,Fhim down. We are going to do what we
OL,15,Fcan to get justice," she said.
OL,17,FDuring the police investigation, a 19-
OL,18,Fyear-old man, and later a 32-year-old
OL,19,Fman, were arrested in connection with
OL,20,Fa collision but no one was officially
OL,21,Fcharged.
