OL,3,CMother's fight to reopen the case of
OL,4,Cher son's death
OL,6,FFrustrated with the answers they have
OL,7,Freceived from the police so far,
OL,8,FMelanie and Josh's sister, Abi, are
OL,9,Fdoing their own investigation and
OL,10,Fresearch.
OL,12,F"During this period where we should
OL,13,Fhave had time to mourn, but we have
OL,14,Fbeen trying to find answers to what
OL,15,Fhappened to Josh. And that is
OL,16,Fsomething we should not have to do."
OL,17,FMelanie added.
