OL,3,CMother's fight to reopen the case of
OL,4,Cher son's death
OL,6,FJosh was originally from Caernarfon,
OL,7,Fand a student at Cardiff Metropolitan
OL,8,FUniversity, where he was a member of
OL,9,Fthe Welsh Association, which has been
OL,10,F"very supportive".
OL,12,FHe was a talented footballer and an
OL,13,Favid fan of Everton and Wales.
OL,15,FThroughout the investigation members
OL,16,Fof Josh's family received support from
OL,17,Fspecialist officers. Melanie said she
OL,18,Fis also "extremely grateful" to the
OL,19,Fcommunity in Caernarfon for their
OL,20,Fsupport and to the charity.
