OL,6,FIn response, a spokesperson for North
OL,7,FWales Police said that as a result of
OL,8,FMelanie's request for a review of the
OL,9,Foriginal investigation, and the
OL,10,Fongoing inquest, it would be
OL,11,F"inappropriate" for them to comment as
OL,12,Fthis could impact any potential future
OL,13,Flegal proceedings or court case.
OL,15,FMelanie and Josh's sister, Abi, will
OL,16,Fnow wait to hear what evidence will
OL,17,Fcome before the inquest.
